subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal advanced to the Swiss Indoors semifinals, beating Marin Cilic, 4-6, 6-3, 6-3, in Basel, Switzerland. He will face Richard Gasquet in a semifinal Saturday.
